<h2>Introduction</h2>

<ModalWorkspace as |workspace|>

  <p>
    I've developed and iterated on the management of modal dialog popups. This
    site is a showcase for those ideas.
    <button class="btn btn-link" {{on "click" (fn workspace.open "example1")}}>
      Try opening this example modal.
    </button>
  </p>

  <p>
    There are several core concepts I employ.
  </p>

  <workspace.modal
    @name="example1"
    {{animated "rotateIn" close="rotateOut"}}
    as |modal|
  >
    <modal.header>
      <h1>Example Modal</h1>
    </modal.header>
    <modal.body>
      <p>This is an example modal dialog.</p>
    </modal.body>
    <modal.footer>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" {{on "click" modal.cancel}}>
        Dismiss
      </button>
    </modal.footer>
  </workspace.modal>

</ModalWorkspace>
